author: Sam Meredith
title: Saudi Arabia is the winner from oil's historic price plunge, analysts say
description: Saudi Arabia will be best positioned to weather the impact of an unprecedented collapse in U.S. oil prices, analysts told CNBC on Tuesday.
content:
